---
import LayoutModern from '../layouts/LayoutModern.astro';
---

<LayoutModern title="Waterloo Track - First-Party Attribution That Actually Works">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>We help you <span class="accent">know</span> which ads actually work</h1>
			<p>Stop guessing. Start knowing. First-party attribution that captures the 30% of conversions your platforms miss.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn">GET YOUR FREE AUDIT</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Problem Section -->
	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Your Attribution Is <span style="color: var(--color-primary);">Broken</span></h2>
			<p style="font-size: 1.3rem; max-width: 800px;">iOS updates killed your tracking. Privacy laws made it worse. Now you're making million-dollar decisions with 70% of the data.</p>
			
			<div class="grid grid-3">
				<div class="feature-box">
					<h3>30% Blind Spot</h3>
					<p>Nearly a third of your conversions are completely invisible to Facebook and Google.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-box">
					<h3>False Winners</h3>
					<p>Platforms take credit for sales they didn't drive. Your worst campaigns look profitable.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-box">
					<h3>Wasted Budget</h3>
					<p>You're scaling losers and killing winners because the data is fundamentally wrong.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Solution Section -->
	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 style="color: var(--color-light);">The Only Attribution That <span style="color: var(--color-primary);">Actually Works</span></h2>
			<p style="font-size: 1.3rem; max-width: 800px; margin-bottom: 60px;">Server-side tracking that captures everything. First-party data you own. Attribution that makes sense.</p>
			
			<div class="grid grid-3">
				<div class="card">
					<h3>For Agencies</h3>
					<p>Turn attribution into recurring revenue. Get credit for your wins. Never lose another client to "poor performance" that's actually just broken tracking.</p>
					<a href="/for-agencies" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600;">Learn More →</a>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>For Business Owners</h3>
					<p>See which ads actually make money in 10 minutes. Stop wasting thousands on campaigns that don't work.</p>
					<a href="/for-business-owners" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600;">Learn More →</a>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>For Marketing Directors</h3>
					<p>Get attribution data that finance actually trusts. Turn data chaos into boardroom confidence.</p>
					<a href="/for-marketing-directors" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600;">Learn More →</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Social Proof Section -->
	<section class="section section-light">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 style="text-align: center;">Real Results From <span style="color: var(--color-primary);">Real Businesses</span></h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-2">
				<div class="card">
					<p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 30px;">"Found $12k/month in wasted spend in the first week. Reallocated it. Revenue up 40% in two months."</p>
					<p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-gray);">E-commerce Brand</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 30px;">"Saved three client relationships by proving our campaigns were actually working. The platforms just couldn't see it."</p>
					<p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-gray);">Digital Marketing Agency</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<section class="section section-dark" style="text-align: center;">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 style="color: var(--color-light);">Ready to See What's <span style="color: var(--color-primary);">Really Working?</span></h2>
			<p style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 50px;">Free attribution audit. We'll show you exactly what you're missing.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn">GET YOUR FREE AUDIT</a>
			<p style="margin-top: 20px; opacity: 0.7;">If we can't find at least $1,000/month in wasted spend, the audit is free.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</LayoutModern>